<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:14:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>欧盟敦促中国停止镇压人权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/eu-urges-china-stop-human-rights-crackdown-2024-06-17/</link><description>在欧盟代表团访问西藏并会见中国官员后，欧盟周一再次呼吁中国停止侵犯人权行为。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/eu-urges-china-stop-human-rights-crackdown-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>丹麦游说团体寻求迅速解决中国猪肉关税威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/danish-lobby-group-seeks-swift-solution-chinas-threatened-pork-tariffs-2024-06-17/</link><description>游说团体丹麦农业与食品委员会周一告诉路透社，丹麦猪肉行业表示，如果中国限制欧洲肉类进口，丹麦猪肉行业将受到沉重打击，并呼吁在 7 月 4 日之前找到解决方案。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 14:39:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/danish-lobby-group-seeks-swift-solution-chinas-threatened-pork-tariffs-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>法庭获悉，英国军情五处向中国发出间谍警报，以转移人们对首相丑闻的注意力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uks-mi5-issued-chinese-spy-alert-divert-attention-pm-scandal-court-hears-2024-06-17/</link><description>英国国内间谍机构军情五处发布警告，称一名女性为中国特工，可能是为了转移人们对涉及前首相鲍里斯·约翰逊的新冠封锁派对丑闻的注意力，伦敦一家法庭周一开庭审理。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 14:14:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uks-mi5-issued-chinese-spy-alert-divert-attention-pm-scandal-court-hears-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>上诉法院将于 9 月 16 日听取对美国潜在禁令的质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/appeals-court-hear-challenges-potential-us-tiktok-ban-sept-16-2024-06-17/</link><description>美国一家上诉法院周一表示，将于 9 月 16 日就一项新法律的法律挑战举行口头辩论，该法律要求中国字节跳动在 1 月 19 日之前剥离 TikTok 在美国的资产，否则将面临禁令。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 14:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/appeals-court-hear-challenges-potential-us-tiktok-ban-sept-16-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>普京会见金正恩时俄罗斯与朝鲜关系的时间表</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/highs-lows-russia-north-korea-relations-under-putin-2024-06-17/</link><description>两国表示，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京将于周二和周三访问朝鲜，并与朝鲜领导人金正恩举行会谈。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:55:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/highs-lows-russia-north-korea-relations-under-putin-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>猪肉出口竞争对手可能受益于中欧贸易紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rival-pork-exporters-could-benefit-china-eu-trade-tensions-2024-06-17/</link><description>贸易商和分析师表示，如果北京因贸易紧张局势升级而限制从欧盟的进口，来自南美和美国的猪肉供应商可能会在中国获得市场份额。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rival-pork-exporters-could-benefit-china-eu-trade-tensions-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称抵制中国在南海的“鲁莽行为”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-resist-chinas-reckless-behaviour-south-china-sea-2024-06-17/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周一表示，该国武装部队将抵制中国在马尼拉声称拥有主权的南海领土上的“危险和鲁莽行为”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-resist-chinas-reckless-behaviour-south-china-sea-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>阿迪达斯股价因中国腐败指控调查而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/adidas-shares-fall-investigation-into-china-corruption-allegation-2024-06-17/</link><description>德国运动服装品牌阿迪达斯在收到一封匿名信后表示正在调查中国的腐败指控，该公司股价周一下跌 4%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 11:40:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/adidas-shares-fall-investigation-into-china-corruption-allegation-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>普京将访问朝鲜，美国和盟友谴责军事关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russias-putin-visit-north-korea-june-18-19-2024-06-17/</link><description>两国表示，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京将于本周访问朝鲜，这是 24 年来的首次访问，这次罕见的访问凸显了莫斯科与这个核武器国家迅速发展的伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 11:14:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russias-putin-visit-north-korea-june-18-19-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国、加拿大、日本和菲律宾在南海举行演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-canada-japan-philippines-conduct-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-06-17/</link><description>美国太平洋舰队周一在其网站上表示，美国、加拿大、日本和菲律宾在马尼拉南海专属经济区进行了为期两天的联合海上演习。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 10:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-canada-japan-philippines-conduct-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国宣布猪肉反倾销调查后西班牙寻求避免贸易战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/spain-calls-negotiations-after-china-announces-eu-pork-anti-dumping-probe-2024-06-17/</link><description>欧盟主要猪肉出口国西班牙周一表示，在北京表示将启动反倾销调查后，该国正在与欧盟官员合作，以避免破坏性关税。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 10:21:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/spain-calls-negotiations-after-china-announces-eu-pork-anti-dumping-probe-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国的乐观情绪关注法国的焦虑，中国的国内困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-graphics-2024-06-17/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 10:09:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-graphics-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>伯克希尔哈撒韦公司减持中国比亚迪股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/berkshire-hathaway-sells-398-mln-shares-chinas-byd-2024-06-17/</link><description>沃伦·巴菲特的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司减持了中国比亚迪的股份，比亚迪去年超越特斯拉，成为全球最大的电动汽车销售商。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/berkshire-hathaway-sells-398-mln-shares-chinas-byd-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>巴西加入竞争以放松中国对稀土行业的控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-joins-race-loosen-chinas-grip-rare-earths-industry-2024-06-17/</link><description>随着西方经济体努力获取用于绿色能源和国防的磁铁所需的金属，并打破中国在供应链中的主导地位，矿业巨头巴西雄心勃勃地建立稀土行业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 08:57:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-joins-race-loosen-chinas-grip-rare-earths-industry-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国对欧洲猪肉展开针锋相对的反倾销立案调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-opens-anti-dumping-probe-into-imported-pork-by-products-eu-2024-06-17/</link><description>中国已对来自欧盟的进口猪肉及其副产品启动反倾销调查，此举似乎主要针对西班牙、荷兰和丹麦，以回应其电动汽车出口的限制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-opens-anti-dumping-probe-into-imported-pork-by-products-eu-2024-06-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>